chakra and there would be a battle

31:25.720 --> 31:28.945
Christ would crucify himself

31:28.945 --> 31:35.215
One crucifiction is better than everyday

31:35.240 --> 31:41.370
Only Mother can do this work
With such a power of love

31:41.370 --> 31:45.943
Anything can be worked out with her power of love

31:45.975 --> 31:52.600
She holds everything with so much love
that children don't mind correcting

31:52.600 --> 32:00.040
For instance when trouble comes only mother
knows how to handle it and scold later

32:00.040 --> 32:05.260
Because children understands mother's love
and it is for them

32:05.260 --> 32:12.970
With father children may react
but not with mother's love without expectation

32:12.970 --> 32:22.105
She doesn't want anything but her children to be good
and get all my powers, all good in me

32:22.105 --> 32:27.165
If mother feels it children will be fine

32:27.190 --> 32:34.640
But some mothers are very interfering
and get involved in everything

32:34.640 --> 32:38.970
She comes always in front
while husband is at the back

32:38.980 --> 32:41.970
Children will be spoiled by it

32:41.970 --> 32:50.043
Under such harmful environment children
can be very emotional

32:50.043 --> 32:55.195
So woman should be behind
and make her husband in front

32:55.220 --> 32:59.880
Whatever husbands do
wifes must help him behind

32:59.880 --> 33:09.270
The source of his power is wife
Then how pure and hard-working she should be

33:09.270 --> 33:16.100
I put everything on woman
because I know you have great powers inside

33:16.110 --> 33:21.090
Look at me as a Mother
I must make everyone saints

33:21.090 --> 33:26.020
Curing many diseases
to make people saints

33:26.020 --> 33:31.170
Did anyone do this job?
Only Ahilya was saved

33:31.170 --> 33:34.435
Jesus saved 21 people

33:34.435 --> 33:37.715
I must have saved 21000 now

33:37.740 --> 33:42.745
Going around the world to do
everyone's job

33:42.745 --> 33:49.435
it's still going on but I don't feel
because of love

33:49.460 --> 33:56.480
Maybe I should put bandhan
as I don't know what kind of people I meet

33:56.480 --> 34:00.960
But as soon as people comes to me
I absorb all the problems

34:00.960 --> 34:08.485
So love acts by itself
I know everything is done by love

34:08.510 --> 34:15.463
I don't feel bad whatever happens
Only Mother can bear the pain

34:15.622 --> 34:24.040
So I want you to grow consistantly
without hurdles

34:24.050 --> 34:32.500
Also men should help their wives fully
Understand and respect them

34:32.510 --> 34:41.811
Until the 2 wheels gets balanced
the chariot doesn't go forward

34:43.110 --> 34:49.625
They both should be the same but
one on the left and the other on the right

34:50.090 --> 34:54.510
It won't work if you change it

34:54.510 --> 35:07.935
It is moving and working
because they are the same but unique

35:07.960 --> 35:22.910
Same in the sense of height
length and width but they work differently

35:22.910 --> 35:27.960
It's the same in our life

35:27.960 --> 35:39.940
Shri Rama didn't think
only about husband and wife

35:39.940 --> 35:45.630
Didn't think only about children and family

35:45.630 --> 35:54.645
Also of brother, sister, mother, father
and everyone as a normal human being

35:54.645 --> 36:01.195
After he thought about society

36:01.220 --> 36:07.380
About public, state and country

36:07.380 --> 36:18.730
As a human being he has shown
human ideals in his activities

36:18.730 --> 36:28.960
The person who loved his wife so much
knew she was pure and hed left her

36:28.960 --> 36:40.755
Now people give so much to their own wife
but they never give to poor people

36:40.780 --> 36:46.645
Otherwise they give to their relatives
It's a disease among politicians

36:46.645 --> 36:56.415
But the one who has wife who is sakshat
devi had to leave her

36:56.440 --> 37:04.980
We must understand it's attachment
to relatives and possessions

37:04.980 --> 37:12.300
In west marriage relation wasn't alright
but after Sahaja Yoga wife became everything

37:12.325 --> 37:20.188
Here leaders had to leave
because their wives were not alright

37:20.330 --> 37:24.770
Their attention got spoiled
by wife's preaching

37:24.780 --> 37:29.019
At least five yogi left
because of their wives

37:29.485 --> 37:40.510
Wives should understand Sahaja Yoga
and their role in it

37:40.510 --> 37:46.250
In this case husbands shouldn't
agree with their wives at all

37:46.250 --> 37:52.210
Tell her that â€œYou talk and move
too much, Be quiet"

37:52.210 --> 37:55.630
You are useless
Your chakras are not alright

37:55.640 --> 38:00.755
She will be alright only in this way

38:00.755 --> 38:07.060
But instead you blame yourself
and obey your wife?

38:07.085 --> 38:10.155
If she tells you to steal, you do it?

38:10.180 --> 38:18.670
Even after Sahaja Yoga you still
have some catches to take care

38:18.670 --> 38:29.670
On the occasion of Shri Rama
Hanuman should be remembered as his great devotee

38:29.670 --> 38:34.150
And how he was busy at his service

38:34.150 --> 38:46.145
He was aware that his life is
for serving Shri Rama

38:46.145 --> 38:53.325
We should have his awereness in Sahaj Yoga

38:53.350 --> 39:00.090
But it doesn't mean you cook food for
me which I don't eat

39:00.090 --> 39:06.425
You trouble me cooking so much
this and that

39:06.425 --> 39:12.425
Don't keep on serving someone forcefully

39:12.450 --> 39:18.610
What we need is zeal to serve (Sewa)

39:18.620 --> 39:22.105
Hanuman didn't serve food to Shri Rama

39:22.105 --> 39:25.508
Delhi people kept on
serving food so much

39:25.533 --> 39:31.360
that I had to tell them
I wouln't come if you don't stop

39:31.527 --> 39:35.310
Do what you have to do

39:35.310 --> 39:39.572
It's bad to force someone to eat

39:39.572 --> 39:43.195
serving one after another

39:43.220 --> 39:47.260
I don't need anything
and I am tired

39:47.270 --> 39:55.039
I told you only flowers
But don't spend too much also

39:55.125 --> 40:02.725
A lot of flowers make me
worry sometimes

40:02.750 --> 40:11.027
Please your Mother in balance
She is a simple woman who don't understand these

40:11.485 --> 40:19.055
We have to learn that zeal to serve is
from Hanuman ji

40:19.080 --> 40:24.020
There is no special service for me

40:24.045 --> 40:31.135
But if you want to serve me
serve to Sahaj Yoga

40:32.840 --> 40:36.340
Serving to Sahaja Yoga is
serving to me

40:36.340 --> 40:40.920
How many realisation have you given

40:40.945 --> 40:44.444
How many did you transform and inspire

40:44.563 --> 40:50.900
But if you say to new people
they have bhoot, they just leave

40:50.925 --> 41:01.760
One gentleman was told he has
3 bhoots in him so he left Sahaja Yoga

41:01.760 --> 41:06.560
he was told number of bhoots even

41:06.585 --> 41:13.344
he believed it because the Yogi
was an authority in the local area

41:13.501 --> 41:17.860
I don't know who
but the person left

41:17.860 --> 41:24.300
So what we have to learn
from Hanuman is the zeal

41:24.300 --> 41:28.180
" Ram kaj karne ko tatpar"
(eager to do Ram's work)

41:28.180 --> 41:32.720
What is our work?
My work is sahaj yoga

41:32.720 --> 41:37.070
My work is sahaj yoga
To raise kundalini

41:37.080 --> 41:41.813
To make people peaceful and lovable
talking about love

41:41.838 --> 41:55.270
Talk about Sahaja Yoga, about chakras
Make them understand

41:55.280 --> 42:02.480
Doesn't mean you start giving lecture
Some people started to give so much lecture

42:02.480 --> 42:08.140
I had to tell them to stop
Otherwise Sahaja Yoga will be finished

42:08.150 --> 42:16.030
Only long lectures
No time for Mother's talk and Aarti

42:16.040 --> 42:20.945
He said he just can't stop

42:20.945 --> 42:25.275
He doesn't know why
"How can I fix it?"

42:25.275 --> 42:28.765
"You put supari (spice) in your mouth"

42:28.790 --> 42:33.760
Then "How much?"

42:33.760 --> 42:37.620
"It depends on the size of your mouth"

42:37.645 --> 42:43.450
"You don't know it even then
how come you talk aobut Sahaja Yoga"

42:43.450 --> 42:46.950
you don't know it even

42:46.950 --> 42:49.500
People like giving lecture

42:49.510 --> 42:56.120
Get on a stage and won't leave a mic

42:56.120 --> 43:02.100
Once with mic they cant't leave
It's a new disease

43:02.100 --> 43:08.850
So you must understand
why to give lecture

43:08.875 --> 43:17.800
There are so many Mother's talk
you can put a tape or video in every program

43:17.800 --> 43:30.670
After people can write question on paper
And ask them to bring it next program

43:30.670 --> 43:34.970
If there are someone
who is sick or in trouble

43:34.980 --> 43:41.780
Now there is a Yogi
He comes to cure in Calcutta

43:41.780 --> 43:49.230
Now he was called to Russia

43:49.240 --> 43:53.572
One person is running like
Hanuman all over to cure

43:53.597 --> 43:58.957
You all can cure
All women can do

43:58.982 --> 44:02.364
All men also
But nobody tries

44:02.618 --> 44:06.920
By giving lecture how many were cured?

44:07.046 --> 44:08.555
I don't know why only one in India

44:08.555 --> 44:09.055
don't know what's the matter
that till now there is only one man in India
who can cure people

44:12.710 --> 44:20.160
In London there are 15~20 people
who can cure and in France also

44:20.160 --> 44:26.502
One should learn working on people
like giving bandhan

44:26.558 --> 44:37.300
No need to invite someone from abroad
Remove Sahaja Yoga badges if you cannot cure

44:37.300 --> 44:42.275
How do you work on others
if you can't cure even yourself

44:42.300 --> 44:48.315
Everybody has got
all the power to cure anyone

44:48.315 --> 44:52.200
Learn to become masters

44:52.200 --> 44:57.170
Instead of inviting someone
They should go out to cure

44:57.210 --> 45:02.693
Just have some courage to work
Nothing will happen

45:02.892 --> 45:12.512
By working, you become deeper like
a tree grows deeper as it expands

45:12.978 --> 45:20.925
Sahaja Yogis are very much different
from Incarnations

45:20.950 --> 45:26.010
They have never worked in society before

45:26.010 --> 45:30.440
Nobody had the power for a mass

45:30.465 --> 45:36.325
Only one to one
Like King Janaka to Nachiketa

45:36.340 --> 45:45.585
But now you all have it
Just grow it, that's all

45:45.585 --> 45:52.470
Cure yourself and others
Understand Sahaja Yoga, you have everything

45:52.525 --> 45:58.190
But still your attention is wondering
What are you running after?

45:58.190 --> 46:04.838
You still don't understand it
Sahaja Yoga is just blessing

46:04.918 --> 46:09.190
You won't be in short of anything

46:09.215 --> 46:14.590
Just work for sahaja Yoga
Even if you don't work you will be blessed

46:14.590 --> 46:20.720
Business or promotion,
this and that

46:20.745 --> 46:27.563
Everyone is blessed and
nothing to give up

46:27.588 --> 46:33.243
Otherwise in time of freedom fight

46:33.430 --> 46:39.486
we were tortured
Lied on ice, got electric shocks

46:39.525 --> 46:44.015
My parents went to jail
Our house was sold

46:44.015 --> 46:51.780
Lived in a hut... had to sacrifice a lot
And you don't have to do it

46:51.780 --> 46:56.750
But not only recieving
You have to give

46:56.756 --> 47:04.088
If one door is open so should be the other one
Only one doesn't work

47:04.107 --> 47:10.816
Everyone reports me
about blessings they got

47:12.055 --> 47:19.010
We must see what we have done for others

47:19.060 --> 47:31.520
But there are many fights for leadership
It's all mother's play

47:31.530 --> 47:35.670
You will know it when you will fall from there

47:35.670 --> 47:42.399
Specially women shouldn't get involved
They fall very soon

47:42.424 --> 47:47.390
And men should know
there is nothing like ministers

47:47.469 --> 47:51.025
This is Mother's play
Don't get involved in

47:51.025 --> 47:59.037
Why I call a leader? It's a play
There are no leaders

47:59.124 --> 48:07.780
It's just a test if you have ego
If you have, you are gone

48:07.780 --> 48:14.550
It will be shown immediately
In Sahaja Yoga everything gets exposed

48:14.582 --> 48:19.453
Even if I say something
it shows on the faces

48:19.469 --> 48:27.192
Once some leaders came and
confessed their mistakes

48:27.248 --> 48:36.860
They have more responsibilities to be
better, sweet, humble and loving

48:36.860 --> 48:41.250
and become close and sharing with everyone

48:41.250 --> 48:50.320
Now on the auspicious occasion of Shri Rama
we must understand what he had showen

48:50.345 --> 48:56.272
Only a bit of it would please our Mother

48:56.310 --> 49:07.445
He was in exile for a long time in Jungle
Walked barefeet, worked so hard

49:07.445 --> 49:11.395
Just to obey his father

49:11.395 --> 49:15.405
Now to obey me
you don't need to go into exile

49:15.405 --> 49:20.690
Not barefeet, nor starving nothing
All are there for you

49:20.806 --> 49:27.290
But you must know how to cure people
in Sahaja Yoga

49:27.290 --> 49:30.770
everything about sahaj yoga

49:30.797 --> 49:35.455
and mostly about love

49:35.480 --> 49:43.240
it's nothing but power of love
Everybody will be benefited

49:43.240 --> 49:49.770
This is not only for special people

49:49.780 --> 49:56.983
This is not only for one country
but for the whole world

49:57.445 --> 50:06.290
Watch how your attention is
If it's disturbed we should correct it

50:06.367 --> 50:13.480
Put the power of spirit in it
Do everything with concentration

50:13.584 --> 50:20.123
And devotion and love will
make you deep

50:20.123 --> 50:27.013
Otherwise there is lots of rubbish

50:27.038 --> 50:34.939
If you wish to stay like rubbish
you know where it goes at the end

50:35.026 --> 50:39.770
If you want to feel you are
specially good capable of anything

50:39.985 --> 50:45.969
First humility, not only towards me
but everyone

50:46.136 --> 50:58.848
Talk humbly with love and show that
people can blossom like lotus in Sahaja Yoga

50:58.951 --> 51:01.445
to spread fragrance everywhere

51:01.445 --> 51:10.050
People will tell me you are wonderful
if you will do it in that way

51:10.050 --> 51:15.171
One day you too will be called as
Maryada Purushottama

51:15.251 --> 51:21.232
You are the temple of Rama
so have it within yourself

51:21.280 --> 51:27.319
Perform puja to it
Take care of your self-esteem

51:27.851 --> 51:36.808
Take the benefit of self-realization
inside yourself

51:36.855 --> 51:41.440
You must have respect and devotion to it

51:41.440 --> 51:49.738
"Now we are realized"
"How can we do wrong, we are yogi"

51:49.810 --> 51:56.430
Soon you will have blessings
immediately

51:56.430 --> 52:02.568
As I am called Rokra devi, you will get
blessing as soon as you assert it

52:02.814 --> 52:12.220
Everyone is getting blessed with it
give it back to the world

52:12.245 --> 52:25.955
Shri Rama used all his powers for the
benevolence of people to show the ideal

52:25.955 --> 52:33.855
You will be surprised to achieve so high
when the time comes

52:33.865 --> 52:41.875
You won't have any disease and
all bad habits will be dropped

52:41.900 --> 52:50.085
You will eat, talk and watch
as much as you need

52:50.133 --> 53:02.462
You will watch your mind
for introspection

53:02.494 --> 53:13.248
"Where is my mind going?"
"I'm a Sahaja Yogi, stop it"

53:14.168 --> 53:18.046
By doing so
you will be in meditation

53:18.071 --> 53:24.403
Your kundalini will be satisfied
and give you blessings

53:24.428 --> 53:27.408
You say,
"Mother what a blessing"

53:27.580 --> 53:32.283
But you have to jump into it
Only then will you know it

53:32.418 --> 53:36.755
Till then you need to work hard

53:36.755 --> 53:42.835
Shri Rama was born
at midnight so let's have puja late

53:42.860 --> 53:49.922
Shri Rama Puja is not
a specially long one

53:50.103 --> 54:01.834
As he is in a human form
he is humanity within us

54:02.086 --> 54:14.595
by which we understand our intellect
and our thoughts get changed

54:14.620 --> 54:21.890
Shri Rama is that
Through him we can change our thoughts

54:21.890 --> 54:28.060
Our nature can change
Because he is our ideal

54:28.060 --> 54:35.481
After achieving his ideals we reach another
because he was human ideal

54:35.530 --> 54:41.710
It is great that God came to this world
in a human form to became our ideal

54:41.741 --> 54:51.515
He has gone through all the hardships
to show us strength to keep Dharma

54:51.540 --> 54:56.223
That is Vishwa Dharma
and the state of yoga

54:56.834 --> 55:00.850
May God bless you all
